WAFER WORKS CORP (6182)  said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 42.68% to NT$322,057,000 from NT$561,843,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales            322,057          561,843    
YOY%             -42.68%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,213,075        2,629,383   
YOY%             -53.86% 
=================================================================
 